WEBVTT

01:43.020 --> 01:46.009
[Love Song in Winter]

01:46.160 --> 01:49.060
[Episode 21]

01:54.100 --> 01:57.650
[No Entry]

01:57.830 --> 01:58.979
I didn't expect so many things

01:59.009 --> 02:00.210
to happen on my business trip.

02:01.460 --> 02:02.540
I shouldn't have let you

02:02.560 --> 02:03.360
go to Ding Jing's funeral.

02:04.230 --> 02:04.900
It's okay.

02:04.930 --> 02:06.090
My injury is not serious.

02:07.290 --> 02:08.289
Not serious?

02:08.410 --> 02:09.240
If there's a scar,

02:09.270 --> 02:10.949
you'll have problems with filming too.

02:11.390 --> 02:12.670
It won't be that bad.

02:13.190 --> 02:14.240
But to be honest,

02:14.310 --> 02:15.110
I didn't expect

02:15.130 --> 02:16.450
that girl to be so strong.

02:16.480 --> 02:17.690
She almost strangled me to death.

02:18.350 --> 02:19.820
Luckily, the police were there.

02:19.860 --> 02:21.250
Otherwise, she would have killed me.

02:21.710 --> 02:22.470
I've dealt with

02:22.470 --> 02:23.570
the media for you already.

02:23.680 --> 02:24.370
Don't worry.

02:24.710 --> 02:25.329
Thank you.

02:26.230 --> 02:27.460
It must've cost you a lot.

02:28.180 --> 02:29.230
You must be heartbroken.

02:29.630 --> 02:30.190
It's fine.

02:31.480 --> 02:32.310
You really don't need me

02:32.310 --> 02:33.070
to visit you?

02:33.630 --> 02:34.970
No need. Don't come.

02:35.190 --> 02:36.320
Aren't you preparing for the drama?

02:36.390 --> 02:37.110
Get back to work.

02:38.060 --> 02:38.530
Yes.

02:38.550 --> 02:39.560
I've been busy lately.

02:39.590 --> 02:40.480
War scenes

02:40.510 --> 02:41.510
are all expensive.

02:41.900 --> 02:42.470
Hey,

02:42.490 --> 02:43.850
is there still hope

02:44.290 --> 02:45.079
for that role of mine?

02:46.670 --> 02:48.200
They called me.

02:48.470 --> 02:50.210
They said the auditions are over.

02:51.880 --> 02:52.660
Don't worry.

02:53.050 --> 02:53.680
If there are

02:53.710 --> 02:54.710
more roles like this in the future,

02:54.730 --> 02:55.940
I'll keep an eye on them for you.

02:58.320 --> 02:58.940
It's okay.

02:59.220 --> 03:00.090
We'll see.

03:01.890 --> 03:03.210
I'll hang up now.

03:12.320 --> 03:16.230
[No Entry]

03:33.270 --> 03:34.370
Professor Yu?

03:36.110 --> 03:37.100
How are you?

03:37.190 --> 03:37.880
Do you feel better?

03:37.900 --> 03:38.860
Does it still hurt?

03:41.150 --> 03:41.870
It doesn't hurt.

03:43.160 --> 03:44.210
I won't die, anyway.

03:45.950 --> 03:47.150
I didn't expect you

03:47.180 --> 03:47.860
to be so strong mentally.

03:48.350 --> 03:49.500
You acted

03:49.620 --> 03:50.760
very calm yesterday.

03:51.470 --> 03:52.390
But to be honest,

03:53.130 --> 03:54.800
I was almost scared to death yesterday.

03:54.840 --> 03:56.040
I'd only encountered fake scenarios

03:56.070 --> 03:56.950
when filming.

03:56.950 --> 03:57.950
I'd never encountered a real one before.

03:59.010 --> 04:00.250
Isn't that good?

04:00.720 --> 04:01.690
Remember it well.

04:01.790 --> 04:02.790
Maybe you can use it

04:02.810 --> 04:04.100
when filming in the future.

04:06.460 --> 04:07.880
Don't you have classes today?

04:08.410 --> 04:09.710
You have time to visit me?

04:12.350 --> 04:13.390
After all, you got hurt

04:13.410 --> 04:15.250
when we arrested the criminal.

04:15.550 --> 04:17.630
I'm here to express my gratitude.

04:17.800 --> 04:19.420
So you came just to see me?

04:21.730 --> 04:23.350
I'm here to visit you

04:23.390 --> 04:24.310
on behalf of the special investigation team.

04:24.580 --> 04:25.680
Alright, you talk a lot.

04:25.700 --> 04:26.490
You're quite spirited.

04:26.530 --> 04:27.230
Lie down.

04:32.970 --> 04:33.710
What's wrong?

04:33.740 --> 04:34.470
I think I pulled it.

04:34.510 --> 04:35.340
I pulled it.

04:35.750 --> 04:37.400
Let me call the doctor for you.

04:37.430 --> 04:38.090
Don't.

04:41.350 --> 04:43.320
I just want an apple.

04:50.159 --> 04:50.960
Can I?

04:59.790 --> 05:00.960
How did you peel

05:00.990 --> 05:01.670
a great apple

05:01.690 --> 05:02.760
like this?

05:03.030 --> 05:04.210
This is the essence.

05:04.240 --> 05:04.940
Eat.

05:05.830 --> 05:06.790
If my mom saw me

05:06.810 --> 05:07.880
peeling apples like this,

05:08.130 --> 05:09.400
I would've gotten spanked to death.

05:10.820 --> 05:11.800
By the way,

05:12.470 --> 05:13.920
didn't you tell your family

05:13.950 --> 05:15.320
about your injury?

05:15.590 --> 05:16.750
They haven't come to visit you.

05:20.030 --> 05:21.400
You're afraid

05:21.750 --> 05:22.950
your mom would be worried,

05:22.980 --> 05:23.580
right?

05:24.550 --> 05:25.150
It makes sense.

05:25.880 --> 05:27.050
I wouldn't tell them if it were me.

05:34.340 --> 05:35.060
Professor Yu.

05:36.380 --> 05:37.110
I have to tell you

05:37.140 --> 05:38.830
I lied to you about something.

05:40.310 --> 05:41.880
When I was taking classes with you,

05:41.909 --> 05:43.550
I made things up when filling out

05:44.360 --> 05:45.630
my family information.

05:46.480 --> 05:47.270
My company thinks

05:47.310 --> 05:48.590
my family background isn't that great,

05:48.680 --> 05:49.310
so they made up

05:49.350 --> 05:50.470
a fake one for me.

05:53.470 --> 05:54.630
My parents passed away

05:54.670 --> 05:55.430
when I was very young.

05:57.250 --> 05:57.990
But I had a great neighbor auntie

05:58.030 --> 05:59.520
who treated me very well.

05:59.770 --> 06:01.150
She raised me up.

06:02.040 --> 06:03.080
She was the one

06:03.110 --> 06:04.300
who named me Yu Bofeng.

06:08.320 --> 06:09.470
To me,

06:09.820 --> 06:11.160
she was my biological mother.

06:14.880 --> 06:15.890
But later,

06:15.960 --> 06:16.870
there was an accident too.

06:16.950 --> 06:18.230
When I was 17,

06:18.710 --> 06:19.590
she also passed away.

06:21.200 --> 06:22.820
I've been alone since then.

06:27.480 --> 06:28.560
But I feel like

06:30.000 --> 06:31.490
I didn't tell you the truth,

06:32.330 --> 06:34.090
so I should apologize to you.

06:36.640 --> 06:37.530
I'm sorry.

06:43.060 --> 06:44.830
Don't be mad at me, okay?

06:47.630 --> 06:48.460
I'm not.

06:54.480 --> 06:55.750
Thank you for your honesty.

06:57.080 --> 06:58.220
I believe

06:58.830 --> 07:00.400
your family in heaven

07:01.030 --> 07:02.790
would be proud of

07:03.450 --> 07:04.520
your current accomplishments.

07:09.440 --> 07:10.280
Don't worry.

07:10.750 --> 07:11.870
I'll keep it a secret.

07:12.560 --> 07:13.780
I won't tell anyone.

07:17.990 --> 07:19.130
Don't think too much.

07:19.890 --> 07:20.850
Take care of yourself.

07:23.600 --> 07:24.400
I'm leaving.

07:29.430 --> 07:30.610
What now?

07:31.480 --> 07:33.380
While I'm hospitalized...

07:36.080 --> 07:37.950
Can you come help me with my studies?

07:41.110 --> 07:41.930
We'll see.

07:43.090 --> 07:44.570
That means you're coming!

07:45.950 --> 07:46.920
You must!

08:08.110 --> 08:09.230
Mr. Wen, coffee.

08:11.540 --> 08:12.110
Mr. Wen.

08:12.500 --> 08:13.870
Director Chen Chang

08:13.890 --> 08:14.950
wants to meet you.

08:15.070 --> 08:16.390
He likes Yu Bofeng very much

08:16.410 --> 08:17.760
and really wants to work with him.

08:18.850 --> 08:19.400
Mr. Wen.

08:20.450 --> 08:21.010
Mr. Wen?

08:23.360 --> 08:24.480
Take a look.

08:25.160 --> 08:26.580
Go on. I'm listening.

08:26.910 --> 08:28.480
Although Director Chen Chang

08:28.510 --> 08:30.520
has just transitioned to filming movies,

08:30.540 --> 08:31.960
he has a good reputation.

08:32.460 --> 08:33.850
This can be

08:33.880 --> 08:34.840
Yu Bofeng's entry point

08:34.870 --> 08:35.950
into the film industry.

08:36.190 --> 08:37.590
He just transitioned to filming movies.

08:38.190 --> 08:39.179
Will anyone invest in him?

08:40.830 --> 08:43.809
Should we meet him or not?

08:45.860 --> 08:46.390
No.

08:47.120 --> 08:48.180
One more thing.

08:48.670 --> 08:50.340
The advertiser called,

08:50.610 --> 08:52.960
saying that our artist Liu Keru

08:52.980 --> 08:54.340
got angry on the set again.

08:56.110 --> 08:57.160
How many times has it been?

08:57.740 --> 08:58.990
Including this time,

08:59.010 --> 08:59.860
this is the sixth time.

09:02.440 --> 09:03.610
When will she come to the company?

09:04.020 --> 09:04.950
2 P.M.

09:07.640 --> 09:08.480
Anything else?

09:10.080 --> 09:11.480
Yu Bofeng's assistant

09:11.590 --> 09:12.520
just called me.

09:12.780 --> 09:13.880
He said

09:14.110 --> 09:15.810
Professor Yu went to see him.

09:16.110 --> 09:16.960
They were together

09:17.000 --> 09:17.910
for a long time.

09:19.820 --> 09:20.830
Did anyone take a photo?

09:21.750 --> 09:22.800
Well, no.

09:23.660 --> 09:24.800
I'm just worried

09:24.900 --> 09:25.630
Yu Bofeng

09:25.630 --> 09:26.790
is getting out of control.

09:27.210 --> 09:28.400
We spent so much money

09:28.430 --> 09:29.380
in promoting him.

09:29.690 --> 09:30.950
If he has any scandals,

09:30.970 --> 09:32.410
will our money...

09:33.340 --> 09:34.940
It's none of your business.

09:37.630 --> 09:38.520
I understand.

09:39.150 --> 09:39.990
Then, Mr. Wen,

09:40.470 --> 09:41.630
if there's nothing else,

09:41.660 --> 09:42.460
I'll get back to work.

09:51.390 --> 09:51.980
Peng.

09:53.790 --> 09:54.640
Why are you here?

09:54.670 --> 09:55.830
I was just passing by.

09:56.080 --> 09:57.800
I brought you two bottles of good wine to try.

09:58.940 --> 09:59.710
Take a look.

10:00.100 --> 10:00.920
[Taste]

10:01.050 --> 10:02.350
[Treasure]

10:01.670 --> 10:03.360
I know you like baijiu.

10:06.270 --> 10:06.980
What's up?

10:07.200 --> 10:08.370
Is something wrong?

10:10.760 --> 10:11.670
Nothing.

10:11.770 --> 10:12.520
Well,

10:12.540 --> 10:14.070
about that movie partnership

10:14.200 --> 10:15.610
you told me last time,

10:16.270 --> 10:17.030
can I still participate?

10:17.520 --> 10:18.530
Are you interested now?

10:20.680 --> 10:21.470
Weren't you trying

10:21.510 --> 10:22.590
to keep things safe before?

10:22.670 --> 10:23.620
What?

10:23.830 --> 10:24.820
You're being ambitious now?

10:25.030 --> 10:26.350
Things are different now.

10:26.790 --> 10:27.760
Tang Jie is pregnant.

10:27.910 --> 10:28.840
I’m going to be a father.

10:29.210 --> 10:30.420
I need to earn some money for the baby.

10:32.130 --> 10:32.940
Congratulations.

10:33.880 --> 10:35.640
This is worth celebrating.

10:35.670 --> 10:36.380
Let's have a drink.

10:36.670 --> 10:37.420
Thank you, Peng.

10:37.830 --> 10:38.570
Well,

10:38.800 --> 10:39.890
when the baby is born,

10:39.910 --> 10:40.890
I'll invite you to the baby shower.

10:41.480 --> 10:42.260
Listen.

10:42.350 --> 10:43.110
There are so many good things

10:43.130 --> 10:43.970
happening lately.

10:44.010 --> 10:45.270
One after another.

10:45.430 --> 10:46.140
Jiang

10:46.170 --> 10:47.320
has made up with Lu Yan.

10:48.140 --> 10:48.950
Maybe one day,

10:48.950 --> 10:50.150
they'll invite us to the wedding.

10:54.310 --> 10:54.960
Peng.

10:55.280 --> 10:55.930
Peng?

10:58.330 --> 10:59.270
Cheers.

11:03.660 --> 11:04.840
Look at them.

11:05.490 --> 11:07.160
After so many years,

11:07.200 --> 11:07.990
it wasn't easy,

11:08.150 --> 11:10.200
but there's finally a happy ending.

11:11.390 --> 11:12.700
I've really fussed over them

11:12.740 --> 11:14.480
with Tang Jie.

11:15.010 --> 11:16.240
I’ve discussed it with Tang Jie.

11:16.600 --> 11:17.780
When my baby is born,

11:17.800 --> 11:19.800
they will be the godparents.

11:20.050 --> 11:20.980
The godfather is a police officer,

11:21.100 --> 11:22.170
while the godmother is a doctor.

11:22.440 --> 11:23.890
This combo of professions

11:23.930 --> 11:24.480
is great.

11:28.470 --> 11:29.130
Zhong.

11:29.480 --> 11:30.460
I have something to do.

11:30.890 --> 11:32.160
I have to go.

11:32.320 --> 11:32.870
How about this?

11:33.290 --> 11:34.700
I'll let you know right away

11:34.730 --> 11:35.530
when there's news about the movie.

11:36.430 --> 11:36.910
Okay.

11:37.020 --> 11:38.160
I'll wait for your message.

11:38.360 --> 11:39.140
I'm leaving.

11:39.300 --> 11:40.030
I'll stop bothering you.

11:40.150 --> 11:40.670
Okay.

11:41.090 --> 11:42.770
Remember to try the alcohol.

11:43.810 --> 11:45.230
I'll wait for your news, Peng.

11:59.330 --> 12:00.900
[Yunyin Ninghai]

12:00.190 --> 12:01.150
Ke, listen to me.

12:01.190 --> 12:02.070
Don't worry, okay?

12:01.880 --> 12:05.520
[Yunyin Ninghai]

12:02.230 --> 12:03.230
I starved myself for two days

12:03.230 --> 12:04.790
for this commercial.

12:04.870 --> 12:05.600
This one commercial

12:05.630 --> 12:06.830
took more than ten hours to shoot.

12:07.220 --> 12:08.100
Are you trying to kill me?

12:08.230 --> 12:08.880
Ke.

12:08.910 --> 12:09.590
Hang in there.

12:09.670 --> 12:11.140
After all, we've signed the contract.

12:11.670 --> 12:13.140
Don't mention the contract.

12:13.270 --> 12:14.130
Listen.

12:14.270 --> 12:15.020
If you won't let me

12:15.070 --> 12:15.960
eat this today,

12:15.990 --> 12:16.770
I won't shoot anymore.

12:16.910 --> 12:17.920
You'll have no one.

12:17.940 --> 12:18.600
Okay, okay.

12:18.790 --> 12:19.470
Calm down.

12:19.700 --> 12:20.790
Leave it to me.

12:20.870 --> 12:22.010
Don’t talk to me.

12:30.780 --> 12:31.590
Mr. Wen.

12:39.730 --> 12:40.400
Wen,

12:40.430 --> 12:41.960
I don't want to do commercials anymore.

12:41.980 --> 12:43.140
I want to act in a movie.

12:43.170 --> 12:44.080
Didn't you promise

12:44.110 --> 12:45.270
to get a movie for me?

12:49.670 --> 12:50.550
Is work tiring?

12:51.190 --> 12:51.770
Yes.

12:51.800 --> 12:52.840
I've even lost weight.

12:59.000 --> 13:00.260
Looks like

13:00.890 --> 13:01.900
I should reward you today.

13:02.670 --> 13:03.390
Really?

13:04.750 --> 13:06.010
I'll treat you to a drink today.

13:07.990 --> 13:08.860
A drink?

13:08.910 --> 13:09.790
Where?

13:12.510 --> 13:13.480
Here.

13:28.460 --> 13:30.370
For last year's costume drama,

13:31.520 --> 13:33.140
you were late 16 times

13:34.510 --> 13:35.850
from the start to finish.

13:36.600 --> 13:37.310
You worked hard.

13:40.210 --> 13:41.080
Wen,

13:41.100 --> 13:42.110
I'm sorry.

14:07.220 --> 14:09.090
At the beginning of the year, I had you be

14:09.110 --> 14:10.410
the leading actress of the company's drama.

14:11.780 --> 14:13.510
Not only did you date,

14:13.790 --> 14:14.770
but you were also photographed

14:15.230 --> 14:16.090
and hit the reporters.

14:16.820 --> 14:18.330
Do you know how much I sacrificed

14:18.360 --> 14:19.270
for this?

14:20.480 --> 14:21.720
Wen, I know.

15:01.030 --> 15:02.290
You don't like shooting commercials.

15:04.560 --> 15:05.610
You like insulting people.

15:08.240 --> 15:09.520
Are you a superstar?

15:16.400 --> 15:17.520
Come on, superstar.

15:18.210 --> 15:19.420
Here's to you.

16:01.210 --> 16:01.990
Remember.

16:03.670 --> 16:04.480
It's not my duty

16:04.990 --> 16:06.070
to be nice to you.

16:07.240 --> 16:08.630
I can promote you.

16:09.960 --> 16:11.070
I can also drag you down.

16:32.750 --> 16:33.640
What are you cooking?

16:34.130 --> 16:34.970
Soup.

16:37.590 --> 16:39.270
Then I'll wash tomatoes.

16:39.320 --> 16:39.910
Okay.

16:45.650 --> 16:47.190
♫As the city flickers♫

16:48.350 --> 16:51.180
♫It's as gentle as wind wrapping around rain♫

16:52.410 --> 16:53.700
♫And you, who love to smile♫

16:54.720 --> 16:57.180
♫Always offer your happiness to me first♫

16:58.210 --> 17:00.550
♫The humor of time♫

17:02.040 --> 17:04.480
♫No one to blame for breaking the promise♫

17:05.550 --> 17:11.310
♫It's because we met too soon that we missed each other♫

17:06.829 --> 17:07.490
Is it good?

17:08.560 --> 17:09.190
What?

17:12.690 --> 17:14.310
♫We're stranded at sunset♫

17:13.310 --> 17:14.250
What?

17:15.420 --> 17:18.280
♫My sunburnt face doesn't mean a word♫

17:19.569 --> 17:21.000
♫The stubborn me♫

17:22.230 --> 17:24.930
♫I always think of the far future♫

17:25.710 --> 17:27.780
♫I walk willfully♫

17:29.160 --> 17:32.080
♫Like a star revolving around♫

17:32.720 --> 17:34.030
♫I turn around♫

17:35.200 --> 17:38.810
♫But you're not behind me♫

17:40.360 --> 17:41.920
♫Losing you♫

17:42.770 --> 17:45.080
♫It's so unreal♫

17:46.140 --> 17:47.560
♫I hurt my love♫

17:48.280 --> 17:49.220
♫But still hope to♫

17:49.970 --> 17:52.670
♫Start anew♫

17:53.860 --> 17:56.060
♫There’s a certain kind of squander♫

17:56.830 --> 17:59.080
♫Where I'm late to know who loves me♫

18:00.510 --> 18:02.680
♫When you're not here♫

18:03.270 --> 18:06.690
♫Life becomes aimless♫

18:07.450 --> 18:09.130
♫I miss you♫

18:10.210 --> 18:12.320
♫It's so real♫

18:13.450 --> 18:14.990
♫The person I trust♫

18:15.570 --> 18:16.670
♫Insists on separating♫

18:17.180 --> 18:20.230
♫Who can explain?♫

18:20.980 --> 18:21.590
Let me see.

18:21.340 --> 18:23.260
♫I'm not afraid of your happiness♫

18:22.030 --> 18:22.790
It's not done yet.

18:22.810 --> 18:24.220
I haven't finished yet.

18:24.310 --> 18:26.520
♫I'm afraid you'll forget me♫

18:24.700 --> 18:25.480
You can't run.

18:27.350 --> 18:29.780
♫To feel my heartache♫

18:28.270 --> 18:29.240
Why are you tickling me?

18:29.310 --> 18:30.260
Why are you tickling me?

18:30.310 --> 18:31.790
No, I'm more afraid of your tickling.

18:30.760 --> 18:32.340
♫When I no longer have the best♫

18:33.380 --> 18:36.560
♫I miss you missing me♫

18:40.790 --> 18:41.440
No, this doesn't count.

18:41.470 --> 18:41.840
What?

18:41.870 --> 18:42.470
Why not?

18:42.490 --> 18:43.170
Give it to me.

18:43.300 --> 18:44.370
You're cheating.

18:49.000 --> 18:50.420
♫When I walk the path you've walked♫

18:51.070 --> 18:54.120
♫Waiting to bump into you on the street♫

18:55.520 --> 18:57.170
♫Like yesterday♫

18:57.910 --> 19:00.540
♫Our forever had no end♫

18:58.910 --> 18:59.610
What's wrong?

19:01.130 --> 19:02.270
Jiang Chengyi.

19:01.710 --> 19:02.900
♫I'm the stupid one♫

19:02.990 --> 19:03.750
Tell me.

19:05.590 --> 19:08.220
♫You've already engraved yourself in my pulse♫

19:09.430 --> 19:15.180
♫I don't want you to disappear like a rainbow♫

19:16.700 --> 19:17.920
♫Losing you♫

19:18.990 --> 19:21.050
♫It's so unreal♫

19:22.400 --> 19:23.730
♫I hurt my love♫

19:24.090 --> 19:25.260
♫But still hope to♫

19:25.170 --> 19:29.020
[Anshan, Ninghai Public Security
Criminal Investigation Unit]

19:31.200 --> 19:31.890
Li Yong.

19:32.130 --> 19:33.830
Is the time correct?

19:34.230 --> 19:34.860
Yes.

19:34.890 --> 19:35.680
Can the time be right?

19:35.830 --> 19:36.440
Okay.

19:41.950 --> 19:42.540
Captain Jiang.

19:42.610 --> 19:43.310
There's news

19:43.340 --> 19:44.270
from Chengzhou.

19:46.540 --> 19:47.790
We haven't found Li Ruonan's mother,

19:47.790 --> 19:48.560
Yan Mei.

19:49.350 --> 19:52.110
[Personal information of Yan Mei]

19:52.640 --> 19:53.430
She went missing?

19:54.770 --> 19:55.500
And then?

19:57.040 --> 19:58.600
Chengzhou is located in

19:58.630 --> 19:59.880
the southwest mountains of our country.

19:59.990 --> 20:00.550
It's a small town

20:00.590 --> 20:02.080
that is poor and backward.

20:02.120 --> 20:03.100
The first highway was built

20:03.150 --> 20:04.110
only a few years ago.

20:04.130 --> 20:05.270
The local Public Security Bureau

20:05.290 --> 20:07.250
only connected to the Internet two years ago.

20:07.760 --> 20:09.280
So, a lot of information

20:09.310 --> 20:10.400
is missing.

20:10.630 --> 20:11.560
In a place

20:11.590 --> 20:13.000
where traffic is so inconvenient,

20:13.320 --> 20:15.370
an old lady like her went missing.

20:15.570 --> 20:17.670
What era is it now?

20:17.800 --> 20:19.850
Is it this hard to find someone?

20:20.940 --> 20:22.600
Since the traffic is not developed,

20:22.910 --> 20:23.880
if something went wrong

20:23.920 --> 20:24.790
in the local area,

20:25.040 --> 20:26.560
she would've been discovered quickly.

20:26.580 --> 20:27.990
She's not here now.

20:28.070 --> 20:28.980
She's missing.

20:29.030 --> 20:30.390
Then she must've been taken elsewhere.

20:31.290 --> 20:33.270
Contact the local police

20:33.590 --> 20:34.350
and find out

20:34.390 --> 20:35.120
what exactly "missing" means.

20:35.150 --> 20:36.270
Trying to appease me with that?

20:36.390 --> 20:37.360
Go find her if they can't do it.

20:37.380 --> 20:38.210
Give me the result in three days.

20:38.310 --> 20:38.930
Got it.

20:50.790 --> 20:51.760
Xiaoman?

20:52.120 --> 20:53.130
Ms. Lu.

20:54.030 --> 20:54.710
Dr. Lu.

20:54.730 --> 20:55.330
Have you eaten?

20:55.460 --> 20:56.150
Not yet.

20:56.310 --> 20:57.440
I'm getting off work.

20:57.460 --> 20:58.840
So I came to visit Xiaoman.

20:59.070 --> 20:59.970
Xiaoman,

21:00.350 --> 21:01.430
you'll be discharged the day after tomorrow.

21:01.470 --> 21:02.500
Are you happy?

21:02.530 --> 21:03.270
No.

21:03.470 --> 21:04.230
No?

21:04.260 --> 21:05.230
Why not?

21:05.410 --> 21:06.460
Mr. Wen said

21:06.490 --> 21:08.000
he'd take me to skate

21:08.050 --> 21:09.450
after I'm discharged.

21:09.790 --> 21:10.950
But he hasn't

21:10.990 --> 21:12.030
come to visit me yet.

21:12.090 --> 21:14.450
Did he lie to me?

21:14.600 --> 21:15.860
Mr. Wen has done

21:15.880 --> 21:17.150
so much for us.

21:17.470 --> 21:18.590
You should be grateful.

21:18.630 --> 21:19.620
Got it, Xiaoman?

21:19.990 --> 21:20.470
It's okay.

21:20.530 --> 21:21.640
I'm calling out Mr. Wen

21:21.670 --> 21:22.810
for you right now—

21:22.830 --> 21:23.590
why didn't he take

21:23.590 --> 21:24.670
our Xiaoman to skate?

21:24.950 --> 21:25.510
Okay.

21:26.350 --> 21:27.530
Who said I lied to him?

21:27.710 --> 21:28.650
Mr. Wen,

21:28.670 --> 21:29.680
are you here to visit me?

21:29.690 --> 21:30.340
Mr. Wen.

21:31.860 --> 21:32.590
Xiaoman,

21:33.120 --> 21:34.100
check these out.

21:36.570 --> 21:37.460
[All-star Skating Club]

21:38.300 --> 21:39.510
The tickets to the skating rink.

21:39.590 --> 21:40.850
Thank you, Mr. Wen.

21:41.150 --> 21:42.390
When you are discharged,

21:42.420 --> 21:43.160
we'll take you there

21:43.190 --> 21:44.070
early in the morning.

21:44.160 --> 21:44.770
Okay?

21:44.940 --> 21:46.460
Okay, pinky swear.

21:46.630 --> 21:47.070
Come on.

21:47.390 --> 21:49.150
-Pinky swear.
-Pinky swear.

21:49.170 --> 21:50.970
-Solid promise.
-Solid promise.

21:51.070 --> 21:51.770
Seal the deal!

21:52.150 --> 21:52.990
Seal the deal.

21:53.310 --> 21:54.790
Okay, it's a deal now.

21:54.860 --> 21:55.740
Yes, deal.

21:56.770 --> 21:57.950
Thank you so much.

21:58.180 --> 21:58.830
No worries.

22:04.880 --> 22:05.970
I'm done.

22:06.520 --> 22:07.810
Sun will arrange work

22:07.850 --> 22:08.960
for you tomorrow.

22:09.230 --> 22:09.590
Yes.

22:09.630 --> 22:09.990
Okay.

22:10.010 --> 22:10.750
Got it.

22:10.790 --> 22:11.430
Clock out! Let's go.

22:11.750 --> 22:13.060
Dr. Han, are you in a hurry to go

22:13.080 --> 22:14.130
for a date?

22:14.260 --> 22:15.750
Shouldn't you be the ones

22:15.790 --> 22:16.750
eager to clock out and avoid me?

22:17.780 --> 22:18.520
Dr. Han.

22:20.000 --> 22:21.080
Jiang, what brings you here?

22:21.230 --> 22:21.910
Come on...

22:21.930 --> 22:22.360
For Lu Yan, huh?

22:22.390 --> 22:22.910
Sit here...

22:22.950 --> 22:23.510
-Sit down.
-Sit here.

22:23.550 --> 22:24.270
I came to pick her up from work.

22:24.270 --> 22:24.790
-C'mon.
-Sit here.

22:24.830 --> 22:25.230
Take my seat.

22:25.270 --> 22:26.110
Don't bother. I'll sit here.

22:28.760 --> 22:30.520
Jiang comes every day.

22:30.540 --> 22:31.650
They're getting on well.

22:31.930 --> 22:32.830
Director Sun.

22:33.510 --> 22:34.460
Well,

22:34.590 --> 22:36.340
does Lu Yan have any time off soon?

22:36.410 --> 22:37.090
Yes.

22:37.510 --> 22:38.340
Certainly!

22:39.190 --> 22:39.670
Let me check.

22:39.690 --> 22:40.160
Okay.

22:42.580 --> 22:43.510
She's got time off this week.

22:43.530 --> 22:44.130
Really?

22:44.150 --> 22:44.750
Great.

22:45.050 --> 22:45.930
What, Captain Jiang?

22:45.980 --> 22:47.250
Are you gonna take Yan on a date?

22:49.080 --> 22:49.750
Captain Jiang,

22:49.790 --> 22:50.680
could you share with us

22:50.710 --> 22:52.360
how you made Dr. Lu your girlfriend

22:52.400 --> 22:53.500
and how you confessed your love?

22:53.790 --> 22:55.350
Well, I didn't...

22:55.710 --> 22:56.230
I'm not sure.

22:56.230 --> 22:57.270
You haven't confessed yet?

22:58.800 --> 22:59.960
I'm experienced in this.

22:59.980 --> 23:00.910
Listen.

23:01.520 --> 23:02.650
Here's my advice.

23:02.670 --> 23:03.460
You gotta...

23:04.180 --> 23:04.920
You

23:04.940 --> 23:06.190
-should prepare
-There he goes again.

23:06.430 --> 23:07.730
99 roses.

23:07.850 --> 23:09.340
That's how kids are.

23:09.370 --> 23:10.400
They need sweet words.

23:11.190 --> 23:12.150
They'll take

23:12.190 --> 23:12.990
every word

23:13.070 --> 23:13.590
we tell them

23:13.590 --> 23:14.550
seriously.

23:14.630 --> 23:16.070
So we can't lie to them.

23:16.950 --> 23:17.910
But,

23:18.470 --> 23:19.390
I'm glad you're here.

23:21.350 --> 23:23.160
[To the Doctor's Office]

23:22.070 --> 23:22.910
Are you free today?

23:22.950 --> 23:24.280
Shall we go to the nearby food street

23:24.310 --> 23:24.940
