23:25.650 --> 23:28.770
I might have to ask for tonight's schedule.

23:37.070 --> 23:38.140
That's it!

23:38.160 --> 23:39.040
You're all here.

23:39.060 --> 23:40.350
Welcome back.

23:40.470 --> 23:41.230
What are you laughing at?

23:41.270 --> 23:42.230
You look so happy.

23:43.130 --> 23:44.270
He's been waiting here for a while

23:44.270 --> 23:45.070
to pick you up from work.

23:45.090 --> 23:45.750
Well,

23:45.750 --> 23:47.400
we were just chatting with Jiang.

23:47.870 --> 23:49.150
I was telling Jiang

23:49.180 --> 23:50.520
how I courted my wife.

23:50.990 --> 23:51.760
Finally, you could tell

23:51.790 --> 23:52.830
the story to someone new to it.

23:53.070 --> 23:54.490
You've all been single for too long.

23:54.520 --> 23:55.630
How can I not be anxious?

23:55.800 --> 23:57.780
I'm even more stressed out than you!

23:58.120 --> 24:00.000
Yeah...

24:00.050 --> 24:00.800
That's so funny.

24:01.880 --> 24:03.280
Peng, you scared me.

24:03.390 --> 24:04.150
Why are you standing there

24:04.170 --> 24:04.770
