24:04.800 --> 24:05.420
Dr. Han.

24:05.450 --> 24:06.750
I'm here to visit Lin Xiaoman.

24:06.780 --> 24:08.000
Visit Lin Xiaoman?

24:08.350 --> 24:10.090
Are you single too?

24:10.110 --> 24:11.080
Good luck!

24:11.930 --> 24:13.050
I'm taking my leave.

24:15.100 --> 24:15.870
Don't forget

24:15.900 --> 24:16.620
the key points

24:16.750 --> 24:18.120
I told you just now.

24:18.150 --> 24:19.160
I'm thinking about it.

24:19.180 --> 24:19.910
Good luck!

24:21.530 --> 24:22.960
What are you guys waiting for?

24:23.590 --> 24:24.390
Want to be third wheels here?

24:24.410 --> 24:25.300
Just go.

24:26.780 --> 24:27.470
Good luck!

24:28.190 --> 24:29.670
Dr. Han must have a date today.

24:30.710 --> 24:31.190
Bye-bye.

24:31.210 --> 24:31.810
Bye-bye.

24:33.440 --> 24:35.250
Let's go. You're off work too, right?

24:37.950 --> 24:39.010
It's my mom.

24:39.070 --> 24:39.630
Mom.

24:40.870 --> 24:41.390
Chengyi,

24:41.470 --> 24:42.870
our iQIYI app

24:42.870 --> 24:43.830
was logged in

24:43.830 --> 24:44.990
with your account, right?

24:45.830 --> 24:47.950
Click the upper right corner.

24:46.910 --> 24:48.630
[Speaker On] [Mic on] [Camera On]

24:47.970 --> 24:48.750
Click it.

24:48.800 --> 24:49.390
Yes, and then

24:49.470 --> 24:50.500
enter my phone number.

24:51.400 --> 24:52.430
Next...

24:52.510 --> 24:53.150
Click "confirm."

24:53.170 --> 24:54.130
I'll send you

24:54.660 --> 24:55.640
the verification code later.

24:55.940 --> 24:56.550
Okay.

24:56.550 --> 24:57.670
Don't forget it.

24:59.330 --> 25:00.520
Well, just wondering,

25:00.800 --> 25:02.510
have you met Dr. Lu recently?

25:02.830 --> 25:03.900
Does she know

25:03.920 --> 25:05.140
you've moved next door to her?

25:04.990 --> 25:13.110
[Speaker On] [Mic on] [Camera On]

25:06.820 --> 25:07.790
Well, mom.

25:08.780 --> 25:09.700
Hello, madam.

25:09.780 --> 25:10.980
Hello, Dr. Lu.

25:11.030 --> 25:11.750
Hello.

25:12.310 --> 25:13.190
Yes, we're in the hospital.

25:14.150 --> 25:15.110
So you're busy?

25:15.560 --> 25:16.430
Okay, good.

25:16.630 --> 25:17.840
I'll leave you to it.

25:17.880 --> 25:18.630
I won't keep you any longer.

25:18.670 --> 25:19.470
Don't forget to send me

25:19.510 --> 25:20.460
the verification code.

25:21.830 --> 25:22.530
I won't forget it.

25:22.670 --> 25:23.510
I'll hang up now.

25:27.270 --> 25:28.180
It was kinda embarrassing.

25:28.210 --> 25:29.350
My car is here.

25:29.480 --> 25:30.270
I'll take my leave.

25:30.990 --> 25:31.670
OK. Bye-bye.

25:31.750 --> 25:32.310
Bye-bye.

25:33.950 --> 25:35.150
I'll go get changed.

25:35.170 --> 25:35.650
Okay.

25:47.670 --> 25:48.310
Mom.

25:48.870 --> 25:49.580
Chengyi,

25:50.160 --> 25:51.260
I'm just wondering

25:51.650 --> 25:52.850
