25:52.920 --> 25:54.410
when I called you earlier.

25:54.440 --> 25:55.330
Nope...

25:56.610 --> 25:57.930
Oh, that's a relief!

25:58.240 --> 25:59.180
Listen,

25:59.710 --> 26:02.220
