26:02.270 --> 26:04.280
especially for Dr. Lu.

26:04.410 --> 26:05.310
Do you hear me?

26:07.270 --> 26:08.110
I know.

26:08.130 --> 26:08.770
I got it.

26:08.990 --> 26:10.090
Don't worry about that.

26:11.830 --> 26:12.510
Nothing else?

26:13.670 --> 26:14.190
Okay.

26:14.830 --> 26:15.470
I'm hanging up.

26:15.490 --> 26:16.270
Okay...

26:32.460 --> 26:33.400
Want some grapes?

26:34.910 --> 26:35.470
Okay.

26:44.960 --> 26:45.560
Here you are.

26:58.790 --> 26:59.760
Are you free this weekend?

27:01.950 --> 27:03.070
