27:09.180 --> 27:10.330
I'll ask my dad to teach you.

27:16.230 --> 27:16.870
No.

27:18.010 --> 27:18.840
Why?

27:20.840 --> 27:22.100
Fine...

27:22.190 --> 27:22.870
But

27:23.600 --> 27:26.940
doesn't that mean I'll meet your parents?

27:28.950 --> 27:29.790
I think

27:31.410 --> 27:32.400
there is a step

27:32.430 --> 27:33.630
