27:35.790 --> 27:37.230
How about I ask my mom to send it to you?

27:37.250 --> 27:38.090
Well...

27:38.400 --> 27:39.190
Don't bother.

27:39.190 --> 27:40.710
I don't wanna trouble your parents.

27:40.940 --> 27:42.020
I mean, a step between us.

27:43.940 --> 27:44.710
Between us?

27:47.000 --> 27:47.810
A step?

27:48.770 --> 27:49.440
Think about it.

27:49.950 --> 27:51.190
So you...

27:53.440 --> 27:54.750
You think

27:55.430 --> 27:56.720
