28:07.510 --> 28:08.130
Yes.

28:09.550 --> 28:10.660
Almost.

28:11.810 --> 28:12.500
Almost...

28:13.910 --> 28:15.050
I see.

28:17.690 --> 28:18.920
Indeed, my bad.

28:19.660 --> 28:20.650
I didn't confess until today.

28:25.430 --> 28:26.030
Lu Yan.

28:28.870 --> 28:29.750
I like you.

28:30.910 --> 28:32.080
Please be my girlfriend.

28:39.150 --> 28:41.810
♫When we're hand in hand, even the equator possesses♫

28:39.840 --> 28:40.450
Well,

28:41.310 --> 28:41.950
