28:42.580 --> 28:45.600
♫Beauty like the aurora and white snow♫

28:44.290 --> 28:44.930
You don't like that?

28:46.760 --> 28:49.140
♫You close your eyes and make a wish, completely defenseless♫

28:47.030 --> 28:47.670
Um...

28:49.760 --> 28:52.720
♫I kiss your face secretly♫

28:49.880 --> 28:50.630
You can't

28:51.150 --> 28:52.550
