28:54.090 --> 28:56.850
♫I long to hold your hands and weave beautiful dreams for you♫

28:57.340 --> 28:58.290
Lu Yan,

28:57.680 --> 28:59.970
♫What we lack is not just time♫

28:58.610 --> 28:59.700
the first time

28:59.740 --> 29:00.830
I saw you,

29:01.550 --> 29:03.270
I was stunned by your beauty

29:01.880 --> 29:04.300
♫Losing sight of the world and our default end point♫

29:04.020 --> 29:05.430
and then fell deeply in love with you.

29:05.170 --> 29:07.550
♫As we write every page of our love by hand♫

29:08.250 --> 29:11.080
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

29:08.450 --> 29:09.530
Please be my girlfriend.

29:10.320 --> 29:12.570
That’s all you can think of?

29:12.210 --> 29:14.770
♫Romance only exists with you♫

29:14.390 --> 29:15.910
Well, Captain Jiang,

29:15.920 --> 29:17.810
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

29:15.950 --> 29:17.480
is that how you usually

29:17.500 --> 29:18.440
interrogate

29:18.730 --> 29:22.030
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

29:18.780 --> 29:19.510
criminals?

29:19.540 --> 29:20.410
Just ask them directly.

29:20.670 --> 29:21.310
No way.

29:21.330 --> 29:22.200
There are skills.

29:22.220 --> 29:23.530
It requires methods and strategies.

29:23.190 --> 29:25.720
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

29:23.640 --> 29:24.760
Tactics may differ depending on

29:24.790 --> 29:26.070
who you're dealing with.

29:26.090 --> 29:27.590
You mean you have a lot to say to criminals,

29:26.810 --> 29:29.440
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

29:27.620 --> 29:28.830
yet little for me?

29:30.230 --> 29:32.450
♫Endless loving and longing♫

29:30.510 --> 29:30.950
You...

29:31.190 --> 29:32.420
How can you

29:32.550 --> 29:33.510
compare yourself to them?

29:33.620 --> 29:34.490
I can't

29:33.670 --> 29:40.750
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

29:34.520 --> 29:35.710
use any tricks on you.

29:35.730 --> 29:37.190
I'm sincere when talking to you.

29:37.470 --> 29:38.310
Fine.

29:46.950 --> 29:47.710
Lu Yan.

29:49.390 --> 29:50.070
Look.

29:52.150 --> 29:52.960
Still not okay?

29:53.800 --> 29:56.500
♫Holding hands while heading to the best outcome♫

29:54.150 --> 29:54.910
Lu Yan.

29:56.310 --> 29:57.070
Lu Yan.

29:57.420 --> 30:00.380
♫Learning the beauty of waiting♫

29:57.890 --> 29:59.500
I like you.

29:59.950 --> 30:00.830
I like you.

30:01.530 --> 30:03.950
♫You know me best, I don't need to speak a word♫

30:02.130 --> 30:03.360
Be my girlfriend.

30:04.410 --> 30:05.380
Let's go to my home.

30:04.920 --> 30:07.510
♫A special thing only you know♫

30:09.140 --> 30:11.800
♫I want to weave a beautiful dream for you♫

30:12.510 --> 30:15.160
♫I'll engrave every fluttering moment♫

30:13.370 --> 30:14.490
Let me think about it

30:16.480 --> 30:18.980
♫I kiss your forehead, as starlight watches us grow old together♫

30:17.140 --> 30:18.260
Think about it?

30:19.880 --> 30:22.370
♫I want to hear you say you don't regret♫

30:21.430 --> 30:22.190
Fine.

30:22.470 --> 30:23.500
That's it.

30:23.040 --> 30:25.710
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

30:25.680 --> 30:26.850
You need to think about it, huh?

30:27.080 --> 30:29.530
♫Romance only exists with you♫

30:27.400 --> 30:27.920
Fine.

30:28.230 --> 30:28.910
Take your time.

30:30.430 --> 30:31.880
I'll help you think about it.

30:30.600 --> 30:32.430
♫Forever and ever into the future♫

30:33.440 --> 30:37.170
♫Let's be super sweet lovers♫

30:38.010 --> 30:40.710
♫How should I describe love, my perfect dear?♫

30:41.740 --> 30:44.320
♫It's my privilege to make you happy♫

30:45.170 --> 30:47.400
♫Endless loving and longing♫

30:48.620 --> 30:55.690
♫Loving you, every day is Valentine's Day♫

31:03.070 --> 31:03.750
Morning.

31:34.140 --> 31:35.030
This way please, Mr. Wen.

31:38.210 --> 31:39.520
You're quite busy, Mr. Wen.

31:46.980 --> 31:48.160
