32:03.160 --> 32:04.400
your father's birthday?

32:10.170 --> 32:11.440
I see, Mr. Wen.

32:11.850 --> 32:13.730
You did this on purpose

32:15.670 --> 32:16.390
to humiliate me,

32:17.430 --> 32:18.030
Right?

32:21.230 --> 32:21.920
Say something.

32:40.890 --> 32:41.690
Who do you think

32:42.530 --> 32:43.870
will come to attend your birthday?

32:44.720 --> 32:45.660
Your friends?

32:47.040 --> 32:47.870
You have no friends.

32:50.620 --> 32:51.850
Or your family?

32:53.080 --> 32:53.800
You don't have one.

32:55.660 --> 32:56.960
You are a lonely old man.

32:59.030 --> 33:00.450
Your wife left you,

33:01.240 --> 33:03.040
and so did your friends.

33:04.070 --> 33:05.640
Almost everyone has left you.

33:10.330 --> 33:11.440
One day,

33:13.230 --> 33:14.460
I will leave you too.

33:19.570 --> 33:20.420
Listen.

33:21.490 --> 33:22.530
I don’t need them.

33:28.580 --> 33:29.210
Mr. Wen,

33:31.240 --> 33:33.520
you can't do whatever you want

33:33.910 --> 33:35.590
just because you're somewhat rich.

33:39.590 --> 33:40.960
You should be glad that I'm rich.

33:41.360 --> 33:42.210
Otherwise,

33:42.870 --> 33:43.880
you wouldn't have a chance

33:44.130 --> 33:45.570
to mess around in such a fancy restaurant.

33:46.550 --> 33:47.510
Instead,

33:48.310 --> 33:49.070
you'd make a scene

33:50.080 --> 33:51.000
on the street.

33:59.750 --> 34:00.320
Dad.

34:01.850 --> 34:02.620
Happy birthday.

34:11.170 --> 34:12.170
I forgot

34:13.800 --> 34:15.639
you've never been happy in your whole life.

35:40.890 --> 35:44.080
[Peng, you can't listen to the voice messages now? I just want to ask you something.]

35:44.100 --> 35:47.110
[Call me when you come back to China, okay?]

35:44.100 --> 35:47.110
[Peng, your Christmas holiday is coming, right? Are you coming back to China?]

35:51.700 --> 35:52.310
Mom,

35:53.200 --> 35:54.600
did he hit you again?

36:00.410 --> 36:01.410
No.

36:05.230 --> 36:06.970
I hit myself by accident.

36:08.570 --> 36:09.520
Mom.

36:10.920 --> 36:12.180
Y-You should go.

36:13.200 --> 36:14.590
Don't ever come back.

36:16.830 --> 36:18.280
As long as I hold Dad off,

36:20.650 --> 36:22.190
he won't have a chance to beat you again.

36:24.890 --> 36:26.300
You've grown up.

36:32.500 --> 36:33.580
I promise you.

36:35.270 --> 36:36.650
I will come back to pick you up

36:37.740 --> 36:39.340
once I settle down.

37:29.570 --> 37:30.930
You did your best.

37:45.320 --> 37:46.400
But no one

37:47.850 --> 37:49.090
will really care about your death.
